# The `SDDbgOperand` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

Holds the information for a single machine location through SDISel; either an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sdnode">SDNode</a>, a constant, a stack location, or a virtual register. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

Holds the information for a single machine location through SDISel; either an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sdnode">SDNode</a>, a constant, a stack location, or a virtual register.
